des:
Freshin Smart Life products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Freshin Smart Life products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Freshin Smart Life" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Freshin Smart Life" app;
(3). You need to have some Freshin Smart Life devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Freshin Smart Life" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Freshin Smart Life" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Freshin Smart Life" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Freshin Smart Life", and you'll be navigated to "Freshin Smart Life" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
